arCallbacks.szOnCallbackCompleteScript:
function Start(idActor, fRange, idActorDetector)
	
	id_Self = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()
	Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(CONVO_VAMP, idActor)
	
end

function Start(idActor, fRange, idActorDetector)
	id_Self = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()
	Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(CONVO_BOSS, idActor)
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	
	id_Self = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()
		
	--Clone Actions
	actorClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(ID_VERA_TRIBE)
	Hydra.QActorWait(actorClone, 1.5)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(actorClone, LOC_BARB, "NPC_WALK", true)
	Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(actorClone, 1)
	
end
